brainf**k interpreter and visualizer in C

installation:
    git clone https://github.com/sleepntsheep/vbf
    cd vbf
    mkdir build
    cd build
    cmake ..
    make
    sudo cp ./vbf /usr/local/bin

** if you're compiling in windows, where ncurses might not be present
    cmake .. -G "MinGW Makefiles" -DHAVE_NCURSES=0

